Respect(Streaming)
===============================================
Respect is one of the most dangerous feeling by a human being for survival of their life. This is an greedy energy generate in the relative environment.
Relativity itself is a energy distributed system/dark system, it always make hindrance when one compare with others energy system.
Respect create the expectation system during its grow. It create the space for maintain the respect.It create the honor.

Social respect(birth to death)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Nothing is static, each and every thing is dynamic and the intensity of every stuff increase/decrease or transformed into another form. It is valid for respect also.

When one get respect?(birth of respect)
--------------------------------
By eye
----------
If one save other's life.
It is a fantastic one but the glow of intensity of this respect also decrease slowly.

By heart
-----------
-If one's action is energetic than others then one get respect form others.The action is dynamic and hence the respect.
-If one get energy(benefit/help..in any form) from others, then one respect to others. It create the expectation for more energy and it make hindrance in respect system.

By thought(auto hindrance)
------------
-If one depends on others, one have to respect others
in fact one need others and respect play a role of emotional hindrance.
-If one have fear from others/one have greedy for others energy/wise system..so on

When respect create, it is in light state and slowly-slowly it transform to dark state.
But one's mind is rigid for respect and that make the hindrance in respect system.

The dark state of respect is nothing but the death of respect.

***Nothing is static but the mind rigid for grow of respect only***

Self respect(streaming)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
It comes from bottom of self heart. It is a solid energy that make your confident to move further on the same path.
It create when one do some fantastic action...like

-Save others life
-A life stone achievement
-Break the rule of society and provide some better solution.
-Invent something
-Be polite in most of the situation
-Handle the situation better than one think.
-Fulfill the responsibility whatever one commit.
...so on.

These all are the solid energy, but one should know every thing transform with time.
If one active towards transformation then it will be fine otherwise the same respect create the hindered to maintain the same one.

***Whatever the thing, it should be light***